orward comparison of tracking system performance using the standard\nMulti Object Tracking (MOT) framework, and classification performance using the\nNeovision2 metrics. These data have been hosted publically.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Apr 2017 02:14:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-24"}
