reated. Applying our\ntheoretical framework, we identify various two-dimensional materials as\ncandidate systems in which stable nodal semimetal phases can be induced via\ndoping, applying electric field, or strain-engineering, etc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Apr 2017 06:55:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-20"}
