chnospheric entities and their\nemergent dynamics for Earth system analysis. Third, we argue that following a\ncoevolutionary approach in conceptualising and modelling technospheric\ndynamics, also including the socio-cultural and biophysical spheres of the\nEarth system, could resolve the apparent conflict between the discourses on\nsustainability and the technosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Apr 2017 10:50:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-24"}
