teristics, and hence adjustment\nfor bias could potentially improve accuracy of meta-analysis results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Apr 2017 11:41:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Nov 2017 17:12:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-28"}
